March, 2023.

New experiences, discoveries, and opportunities. A "POOF" haircut, many "HOW EVEN" skies and sunsets, and other great events.

I've been too lazy to post here, but as a general update, I've passed my first semester (somehow). Classes keep going on, and March was a roller coaster, but a good one overall.

I'm excited for April, but mujhe ghar jaana hai.
